<aura:documentation>
    <aura:description>
        <p>A <code>FinServ:referralSummary</code> component renders referral information about a contact.</p>
        <p>This component can be added to all pages, if the page does not reference a referrer, it pulls summary information for the user.</p>
        <p>Here is an example:</p>
        <pre>&lt;FinServ:referralSummary /></pre>
    </aura:description>
</aura:documentation>